    "plan_content": "Here is the complete implementation plan for the PulseBoard channel plugin.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**17 new files** will be created under `extensions/pulseboard/`. No existing files are modified.\n\n### Structure (mirrors `extensions/irc/`)\n\n```\nextensions/pulseboard/\n├── package.json                 # @openclaw/pulseboard, channel metadata\n├── openclaw.plugin.json         # id: \"pulseboard\", channels: [\"pulseboard\"]\n├── index.ts                     # defineChannelPluginEntry(...)\n├── setup-entry.ts               # defineSetupPluginEntry(...)\n├── api.ts                       # re-exports accounts + setup-core\n└── src/\n    ├── types.ts                 # PulseboardAccountConfig, CoreConfig, PulseboardProbe\n    ├── config-schema.ts         # Zod schema via buildChannelConfigSchema\n    ├── normalize.ts             # normalizePulseboardTarget, isBoardTarget\n    ├── runtime-api.ts           # thin barrel (re-exports from openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc)\n    ├── runtime.ts               # createPluginRuntimeStore\n    ├── accounts.ts              # resolvePulseboardAccount, listPulseboardAccountIds\n    ├── probe.ts                 # probePulseboard (stub)\n    ├── send.ts                  # sendMessagePulseboard (stub)\n    ├── setup-core.ts            # pulseboardSetupAdapter, setPulseboardDmPolicy\n    ├── setup-surface.ts         # pulseboardSetupWizard (4 text inputs)\n    ├── channel.ts               # pulseboardPlugin via createChatChannelPlugin\n    └── channel.test.ts          # 7 Vitest unit tests\n```\n\n### Key design decisions\n\n| Concern | Decision |\n|---|---|\n| Chat types | `[\"direct\", \"group\"]` — DMs (username) and boards (`#board-name`) |\n| Text chunk limit | **4,000 chars**, `chunkerMode: \"markdown\"` |\n| Delivery | `deliveryMode: \"direct\"`, `blockStreaming: true` |\n| Auth fields | `apiKey` (env: `PULSEBOARD_API_KEY` / file / config) + `serverUrl` + `username` |\n| `configured` flag | True only when all three auth fields are non-empty |\n| `runtime-api.ts` source | Re-exports generic channel utilities from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc` (no `pulseboard` SDK facade exists yet) |\n| Gateway | Stub monitor loop that correctly respects `abortSignal` |\n| Local imports | All use `.js` extension (ESM requirement) |\n\n### Verification\n```\npnpm tsgo\npnpm check\npnpm test -- extensions/pulseboard/src/channel.test.ts\npnpm openclaw channels list\n```",
